wikipedia_page.main: Jesse Thomas Williams  ((1903-06-24)24 June 1903 – 20 October 1972) was a Welsh international footballer. He was part of the Wales national football team, playing 1 match on 18  April 1925 against Ireland.He also made appearances in the Football League for Wrexham, Middlesbrough and Clapton Orient.
